<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Sun, 26 Dec 2021 02:27:08 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>非法控制逾 200 個網路鏡頭被捕，中國男稱偷窺別人私隱最興奮</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/26/200camchina/tech-secure/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=200camchina</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sun, 26 Dec 2021 02:25:28 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[資訊保安]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1077273</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>中國一名 24 歲男士涉嫌非法使用電腦，控制逾 200 個網路鏡頭而被當地警方拘捕。 &#160; 警方指 2 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>中國一名 24 歲男士涉嫌非法使用電腦，控制逾 200 個網路鏡頭而被當地警方拘捕。</p><p>警方指 24 歲報稱無業的李姓男子，於今年 4 月起在網上分 5 次購買逾 200 個網路鏡頭控制權，被偷窺及監視的人數過千人，涉事鏡頭分別裝在浴室、酒店、醫院等地。據了解，李會將鏡頭分類以便偷窺，至今共登錄 7500 次鏡頭帳戶，長達 400 多小時。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/ac6d01caly4gxd7r9s4h1j20g407sjrv.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1077281" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/ac6d01caly4gxd7r9s4h1j20g407sjrv.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="280" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/8b0-etnHb4JhhLO_Uynk38dwe9-FFHqRjluKro5biq4.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1077274" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/8b0-etnHb4JhhLO_Uynk38dwe9-FFHqRjluKro5biq4-561x580.jpeg" alt="" width="561" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/8b0-etnHb4JhhLO_Uynk38dwe9-FFHqRjluKro5biq4-561x580.jpeg 561w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/8b0-etnHb4JhhLO_Uynk38dwe9-FFHqRjluKro5biq4-870x900.jpeg 870w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/8b0-etnHb4JhhLO_Uynk38dwe9-FFHqRjluKro5biq4-768x794.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/8b0-etnHb4JhhLO_Uynk38dwe9-FFHqRjluKro5biq4.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 561px" /></a></p><p>李稱對長期在家感到無聊，便沉迷於網路世界中，且認為偷窺別人隱私最興奮，比色情影片更能滿足其慾望。他向警方表示於今年 4 月收到稱「有刺激的影片，要不要，能滿足你的一切慾望」、「很刺激，你想看哪裡的，就有哪裡的，給你不一樣的感覺」的訊息，便首次在網上買下鏡頭帳戶，部分帳戶則是與別人交換而得。</p><p>隨後警方根據李的供詞將首次向他兜售鏡頭帳戶的雷姓男子緝捕拘留，雷表示大多數帳戶的密碼安全性不足，僅使用初始或較簡單的密碼，其所持帳戶皆於網上掃描而得。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Uk7euE48seAG8KLzIQvYlImoBkOfPAumjDEyc4wxMnM.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1077275" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Uk7euE48seAG8KLzIQvYlImoBkOfPAumjDEyc4wxMnM-694x580.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Uk7euE48seAG8KLzIQvYlImoBkOfPAumjDEyc4wxMnM-694x580.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Uk7euE48seAG8KLzIQvYlImoBkOfPAumjDEyc4wxMnM-1075x900.jpeg 1075w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Uk7euE48seAG8KLzIQvYlImoBkOfPAumjDEyc4wxMnM-768x643.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Uk7euE48seAG8KLzIQvYlImoBkOfPAumjDEyc4wxMnM.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>警方提醒網路鏡頭用家應避免使用初始或較易估中的密碼，建議於密碼中加入大細階及數字符號。除了應定期更改密碼外，亦要定期更新軟件及硬件，保障安全，以防有心人入侵用作偷窺及勒索詐騙。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://weibo.com/ttarticle/p/show?id=2309404714272348569897"><span style="color: #262626; font-family: 'Songti TC';">十堰網警巡查執法</span></a></p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
